Key Learnings

- Different Claude models are suitable for different tasks.
- Sonnet is ideal for everyday use.
- Haiku is useful for quick tasks.
- Opus is suitable for advanced reasoning.
- Choosing the right effort level improves efficiency and output quality.
- Context and prompt quality significantly affect AI responses.

